PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1992-3/1057 which will permit the CITY OF SAINTE-AGATHE-DES-MONTS to pay the purchase price for the property situate at 83 St. Vincent Street in Sainte-Agathe-des-Monts, Quebec, over a three-year period, without interest.
